For another left-wing perspective on Lebanon, see <a href="http://www.isreview.org/issues/52/achcar.shtml" target="_blank">"Lebanon and the Middle East Crisis,"</a> an interview with Gilbert Achcar published by the <i>International Socialist Review</i>.
